---
title: Premium Fillet Steak & Tarragon Sauce with Parmesan Mash & Pan-Seared Garlic Greens
description: Make a flavour-packed sauce to drizzle over a tender cut of premium fillet steak using eschalot – a sweeter and more delicate type of onion – plus tarragon and garlic. Then, finish off your gourmet creation with creamy mash and vibrant greens.
